These are Puzzles for 3x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-1::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: crime, romance, zombie, animation, documentary, drama, time-travel
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: trance, pop, indie, punk, ambient, dubstep, hip-hop
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: cricket, lacrosse, skiing, cycling, biathlon, badminton, soccer
 1. the person watching documentary movies is on the far left##1
 2. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the person watching crime movies##1
 3. the person who's sport is soccer is between the fan of pop and the fan of trance##2
 4. the person watching animation movies is on the left of the person who's sport is badminton##1
 5. the fan of pop is on the left of the person watching romance movies##1
 6. the person watching crime movies is the person who's sport is soccer##1
 7. the fan of punk is between the person who's sport is cycling and the person watching documentary movies##2
 8. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left of the person who's sport is badminton##1
 9. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left of the person who's sport is cricket##1
10. the person watching time-travel movies is the fan of indie##1
11. the fan of dubstep is the person watching animation movies##1
12. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left of the person watching zombie movies##1
13. the person who's sport is cricket is the fan of ambient##1
14. the person watching drama movies is between the person who's sport is skiing and the person who's sport is soccer##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |     3      |    4     |   5    |     6      |    7     |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | crime     | drama | romance | animation | time-travel  | zombie  |
| Music-Genre   | trance  | punk        | pop  | hip-hop     | dubstep   | indie       | ambient   |
| Sport         | lacrosse   | soccer | cycling    | skiing  | biathlon | badminton | cricket |

