.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-2::.
There are 7 different nationalities: german, russian, nigerian, argentine, australian, french, turkish
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: surfing, skateboarding, water-polo, volleyball, biathlon, rowing, lacrosse
The people use 7 different means of transport: snowmobile, airplane, skateboard, van, motorbike, jet-ski, bike
 1. the russian is on the right of the person driving the airplane##1
 2. the person who's sport is biathlon is the person who's sport is biathlon##1
 3. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
 4. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1
 5. the person who's sport is surfing is the turkish##1
 6. the german is the person driving the van##1
 7. the german is between the person who's sport is lacrosse and the person driving the bike##2
 8. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left of the australian##1
 9. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
10. the nigerian is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
11. the australian is on the right of the german##1
12. the person driving the snowmobile is the russian##1
13. the argentine is on the left of the german##1
14. the argentine is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1
15. the russian is on the far right##1
16. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left of the turkish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3       |    4     |   5    |     6     |    7     |
| Nationality   | french | turkish      | argentine     | german  | australian | nigerian | russian |
| Sport         | skateboarding  | surfing | rowing | water-polo | lacrosse | volleyball   | biathlon  |
| Transport     | skateboard   | jet-ski     | bike        | van  | motorbike   | airplane       | snowmobile      |

