 8. the person driving the airplane is on the left of the bartender##1
 9. the person driving the tram is on the far right##1
10. the videographer is on the right of the chef##1
11. the person driving the motorbike is the scientist##1
12. the videographer is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
13. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the fisherman##1
14. the person driving the tram is the person drinking cola##1
