11. the person watching romance movies is the polish##1
12. the person eating garlic is the brazilian##1
13. the german is on the far right##1
14. the person watching mystery movies is between the person watching romance movies and the person watching spy movies##2
15. the person eating kiwi is on the right of the person watching western movies##1

