.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-16::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  project-manager, mechanic, designer, journalist, dressmaker, chef, police-officer
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: techno, country, jazz, hip-hop, soul, ambient, classical
7 different pets are kept: turtle, cat, frog, goldfish, dog, horse, pony
 1. the owner of the horse is on the left of the designer##1
 2. the owner of the horse is between the fan of soul and the fan of jazz##2
 3. the fan of techno is the owner of the cat##1
 4. the fan of classical is on the left of the chef##1
 5. the fan of techno is the project-manager##1
 6. the designer is in the middle##1
 7. the dressmaker is the fan of ambient##1
 8. the owner of the cat is on the right of the owner of the pony##1
 9. the fan of techno is the owner of the cat##1
10. the police-officer is the owner of the dog##1
11. the project-manager is on the right of the journalist##1
12. the fan of classical is on the left of the chef##1
13. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
14. the fan of country is on the left of the project-manager##1
15. the police-officer is on the right of the fan of soul##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |      2       |    3     |     4      |    5     |    6    |     7      |
| Job           | mechanic | chef | dressmaker | designer  | police-officer   | journalist | project-manager      |
| Music-Genre   | classical | jazz        | ambient    | soul     | hip-hop     | country   | techno        |
| Pet           | turtle   | frog       | horse    | goldfish | dog | pony   | cat |

