.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-17::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: filmmaking, drawing, puzzles, skydiving, magic-tricks, collecting, reading
7 different pets are kept: hamster, goat, pony, snake, rabbit, ferret, chinchilla
The people use 7 different means of transport: bus, helicopter, motorbike, roller, van, train, car
 1. the person driving the car is between the person who's hobby is drawing and the person who's hobby is filmmaking##2
 2. the person driving the car is the owner of the goat##1
 3. the owner of the rabbit is in the middle##1
 4. the person driving the helicopter is on the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
 5. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
 6. the owner of the pony is on the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
 7. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
 8. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
 9. the owner of the hamster is the person driving the van##1
10. the person driving the roller is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1
11. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
12. the person who's hobby is reading is the owner of the rabbit##1
13. the person driving the roller is the owner of the ferret##1
14. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is the person driving the bus##1
15. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person who's hobby is collecting##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |      2      |     3      |      4      |    5    |   6    |   7    |
| Hobby       | puzzles  | collecting | skydiving  | reading | drawing | magic-tricks | filmmaking |
| Pet         | snake | pony    | hamster        | rabbit      | ferret     | goat   | chinchilla |
| Transport   | motorbike  | helicopter   | van | train        | roller    | car  | bus   |

