.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-18::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: musical, time-travel, martial-arts, animation, mystery, sports, fantasy
7 different pets are kept: turtle, snake, frog, lizard, rat, dog, bird
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: ice-hockey, climbing, cricket, golf, soccer, water-polo, rugby
 1. the owner of the bird is on the left of the person watching sports movies##1
 2. the owner of the rat is on the right of the person who's sport is climbing##1
 3. the person who's sport is rugby is on the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
 4. the person watching mystery movies is on the right of the person watching time-travel movies##1
 5. the person watching musical movies is on the right of the person who's sport is climbing##1
 6. the person who's sport is climbing is in the middle##1
 7. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
 8. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
 9. the person watching sports movies is between the person watching mystery movies and the person who's sport is soccer##2
10. the owner of the dog is on the left of the person who's sport is soccer##1
11. the person watching time-travel movies is the owner of the lizard##1
12. the person watching sports movies is in the middle##1
13. the person watching fantasy movies is on the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
14. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1
15. the person who's sport is cricket is the person watching mystery movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |    3     |     4      |     5     |    6     |     7      |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy   | time-travel    | mystery  | sports        | musical | martial-arts | animation     |
| Pet           | snake | lizard | bird     | dog      | rat     | turtle     | frog    |
| Sport         | ice-hockey   | water-polo  | cricket | climbing | soccer    | golf  | rugby |

