.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-19::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  freelancer, lawyer, engineer, journalist, pilot, librarian, coach
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: western, thriller, martial-arts, animation, fantasy, mystery, musical
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: biathlon, weightlifting, swimming, badminton, baseball, skateboarding, climbing
 1. the journalist is on the left of the coach##1
 2. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
 3. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the person watching thriller movies##1
 4. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the person watching thriller movies##1
 5. the librarian is the person who's sport is climbing##1
 6. the coach is on the right of the person watching fantasy movies##1
 7. the person watching animation movies is on the left of the person watching thriller movies##1
 8. the person who's sport is badminton is on the right of the person watching western movies##1
 9. the person watching animation movies is in the middle##1
10. the person watching mystery movies is on the right of the person who's sport is swimming##1
11. the person watching western movies is on the left of the lawyer##1
12. the person who's sport is biathlon is between the engineer and the person who's sport is skateboarding##2
13. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the person watching thriller movies##1
14. the person watching western movies is the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
15. the freelancer is on the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |      4      |      5       |      6      |      7       |
| Job           | engineer      | freelancer | pilot | lawyer   | librarian | journalist | coach |
| Movie-Genre   | musical | martial-arts   | western   | animation | thriller        | fantasy       | mystery       |
| Sport         | weightlifting    | biathlon       | skateboarding   | badminton      | climbing   | swimming  | baseball |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-20::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, tea, mirinda, juice, milk, soy-milk, water
The people have 7 different hobbies: hiking, video-games, drawing, card-games, cooking, fishing, camping
7 different pets are kept: horse, hamster, hedgehog, fish, turtle, dog, chinchilla
 1. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
 2. the owner of the dog is in the middle##1
 3. the person drinking tea is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1
 4. the person drinking water is the person who's hobby is hiking##1
 5. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the far right##1
 6. the owner of the dog is the person drinking juice##1
 7. the owner of the hedgehog is the person who's hobby is fishing##1
 8. the owner of the fish is between the person who's hobby is drawing and the owner of the hedgehog##2
 9. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the owner of the hamster##1
10. the person who's hobby is card-games is in the middle##1
11. the person drinking milk is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1
12. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
13. the owner of the fish is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
14. the person who's hobby is video-games is between the owner of the chinchilla and the person who's hobby is camping##2
15. the owner of the chinchilla is the person drinking water##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2      |    3    |      4      |     5      |      6      |     7     |
| Beverage   | water  | soy-milk   | milk   | juice        | mirinda     | tea | hot-chocolate       |
| Hobby      | hiking | video-games | camping | card-games | drawing  | cooking   | fishing |
| Pet        | chinchilla   | hamster     | horse     | dog      | turtle | fish    | hedgehog      |

 